sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant SYM as Symbolic Editor (Ontology/Policies/KPIs)
  participant BR as Bridge (DSL, Registry, Generators)
  participant CD as CI/CD + Migrations
  participant RT as Runtime (SCs, Services, Stream, DB)
  participant OBS as Observability (TSDB, Dashboards)

  SYM->>BR: Commit symbolic change (ontology, policy, KPI model)
  BR->>BR: Validate DSL and mappings
  BR->>BR: Generate schemas and guards
  BR->>CD: Emit build artifacts (contracts, services, pipelines)
  CD->>RT: Deploy & migrate (versioned rollout)
  RT-->>OBS: Emit events and metrics
  OBS-->>SYM: KPIs, radar axes, heatmap trends
  SYM-->>SYM: Adjust policies or ontology (next loop)